::Stratus::

"Ok," Stratus replies, walking over to the box and getting an energon 
cube, then putting it into Astroblast's fuel compartment. He was 
beginning to get sick of following these bots' commands, but he was 
here to study, not to cause trouble.


--- In nbwrpg@y..., "rAuq" <rauq@t...> wrote:
> ::Astroblast::
> "Who am I carrying besides some scraps?" Astroblasts voice 
> comes out of the speakers. His control panels show depleting 
> energon supply, and there was conveniently somebot on board to 
> fix the problem. "You, yah you, get the energon cube from the 
> storage box in the corner, and put it in the fuel compartment, 
here." 
> A red light flickers on behind the control room seating as 
> Astroblast finishes.
